video.title: Samaneri Jayasara - Guided Meditation on Awareness (from 'Live' Sangha Meeting) - Extended Version
video.description:
This is the guided meditation I gave - extracted from the recent "Livestream" sangha meeting  held on Christmas morning - for those who have requested it. There are now more silent spaces so that you can enjoy a longer meditation.

May you all have a peaceful and happy New Year and stay safe and well.

With much metta 🌺💜
